        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 13:2",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " he stirred up, and worked upon the corruptions of his heart; suggested evil things to his mind, and baited his temptations agreeable to his malice and covetousness: and this man was ",
        "children": []
